---
title: Peking-Style Tofu & Sweet Chilli Pumpkin Salad with Ginger Dressing & Peanuts
description: There’s a reason they call it dressing – salad would be naked without it! This one uses a clever technique of pouring hot oil over grated ginger and garlic – the oil cooks the aromatic ingredients and creates a unique mixture that you’ll want to drizzle over everything.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5bce9dfb30006c67e0575603-0d186d8f.jpg
